## Code Snippets and Context

### Simplified Header Template

```php
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull has-filter is-style-default has-transparent-background-color has-background" style="border-bottom-style:none;border-bottom-width:0px">
  <!-- Notification bar -->
  <div class="wp-block-group alignfull is-style-light">
    <p class="aligncenter">Save 50% on all products for a limited time â†’</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Main header content -->
  <div class="wp-block-group alignfull" style="padding:var(--wp--preset--spacing--xxs)">
    <div class="wp-block-group alignwide" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(12,minmax(0,1fr))">
      <div class="wp-block-group" style="grid-column:1/3">
        <a href="<?php echo esc_url(home_url('/')); ?>" class="wp-block-site-title">Your Site</a>
      </div>
      <div class="wp-block-group" style="grid-column:3/11;display:flex;justify-content:center">
        <nav class="wp-block-navigation">
          <?php
          wp_nav_menu(array(
            'theme_location' => 'primary', 
            'menu_id'        => 'primary-menu',
          ));
          ?>
        </nav>
      </div>
      <div class="wp-block-group" style="grid-column:11/13;display:flex;justify-content:flex-end">
        <button class="search-toggle">Search</button>
        <button class="dark-mode-toggle">Dark Mode</button>
        <a href="#" class="btn login">Log In</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn signup">Sign Up</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

